@startuml
hide footbox
actor "Admin" as Admin
boundary "AccountListPage.jsx" as ListUI
control "account_detail_api" as API
entity "TaiKhoan" as Acc
entity "NhanVien" as Emp

Admin -> ListUI: Click nút "Xóa"
activate ListUI
ListUI --> Admin: Hộp thoại xác nhận?

Admin -> ListUI: Đồng ý
ListUI -> API: DELETE /api/accounts/{id}/detail/
activate API

alt Thành công
    API -> Emp: Unlink Employee (set user=NULL)
    activate Emp
    Emp --> API: Success
    deactivate Emp

    API -> Acc: Delete User
    activate Acc
    Acc --> API: Success
    deactivate Acc
    
    API --> ListUI: {success: true}
    ListUI --> ListUI: Reload danh sách
    ListUI --> Admin: Cập nhật bảng
else Lỗi
    API --> ListUI: {error: "..."}
    ListUI --> Admin: Hiển thị lỗi
end

deactivate API
deactivate ListUI

@enduml
